name: Big 'ol pouch
description:
Made from 5 oz pecan nut, veg tan leather. Stitched with waxed nylon thread and finished by hand. Our Big 'ol pouch is perfect for storing your essentials, whether that's a mini moleskin and some pens, your passport and tickets or if you're loaded a big stack of 50's.

- Dimensions - 215mm x 115mm
- Handmade in Scotland
- Premium 5oz veg tan leather

Our products are handmade to order and will be dispatched within 10 days from order.

All orders are sent using Royal Mail tracked delivery, please contact us for international postage.
